---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Richad's Blog" description="Learn more about Richad, a 14-year-old mathematics enthusiast">
	<section class="about-hero">
		<div class="about-content">
			<div class="profile-section">
				<div class="profile-image">
					<div class="avatar">
						<span class="avatar-text">R</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="profile-info">
					<h1 class="profile-name">Richad</h1>
					<p class="profile-tagline">14-year-old Mathematics Enthusiast</p>
					<div class="profile-stats">
						<div class="stat">
							<span class="stat-number">14</span>
							<span class="stat-label">Years Old</span>
						</div>
						<div class="stat">
							<span class="stat-number">3+</span>
							<span class="stat-label">Years Learning</span>
						</div>
						<div class="stat">
							<span class="stat-number">50+</span>
							<span class="stat-label">Problems Solved</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-details">
		<div class="details-container">
			<div class="details-grid">
				<div class="detail-card">
					<h2>My Story</h2>
					<p>
						Hi! I'm Richad, a 14-year-old student with an insatiable curiosity for mathematics. 
						My journey with math began when I was 11, and since then, I've been captivated by 
						the beauty and logic of mathematical concepts.
					</p>
					<p>
						What started as simple arithmetic has evolved into a deep appreciation for algebra, 
						geometry, and even early calculus concepts. I believe that mathematics is not just 
						about numbers and formulas‚Äîit's about problem-solving, logical thinking, and 
						discovering patterns in the world around us.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="detail-card">
					<h2>What I'm Learning</h2>
					<div class="learning-list">
						<div class="learning-item">
							<span class="learning-icon">üìê</span>
							<div>
								<h3>Algebra & Functions</h3>
								<p>Exploring quadratic equations, polynomials, and function transformations</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="learning-item">
							<span class="learning-icon">üìä</span>
							<div>
								<h3>Geometry & Trigonometry</h3>
								<p>Understanding shapes, angles, and the relationships between them</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="learning-item">
							<span class="learning-icon">‚à´</span>
							<div>
								<h3>Pre-Calculus</h3>
								<p>Building foundations for limits, derivatives, and integrals</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="learning-item">
							<span class="learning-icon">üî¢</span>
							<div>
								<h3>Number Theory</h3>
								<p>Investigating prime numbers, divisibility, and mathematical proofs</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="detail-card">
					<h2>My Goals</h2>
					<ul class="goals-list">
						<li>Master calculus concepts before graduating high school</li>
						<li>Participate in mathematics competitions and olympiads</li>
						<li>Help other students understand and appreciate mathematics</li>
						<li>Explore the connections between math and other sciences</li>
						<li>Continue sharing my learning journey through this blog</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="detail-card">
					<h2>Why I Blog</h2>
					<p>
						I started this blog to document my mathematical journey and share what I learn 
						with others. Mathematics can seem intimidating, but I believe that with the right 
						approach and explanation, anyone can understand and enjoy it.
					</p>
					<p>
						Through my posts, I aim to break down complex concepts into digestible pieces, 
						share problem-solving strategies, and hopefully inspire other young people to 
						see the beauty in mathematics. Learning is always better when shared!
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="interests">
		<div class="interests-container">
			<h2 class="section-title">Beyond Mathematics</h2>
			<div class="interests-grid">
				<div class="interest-card">
					<div class="interest-icon">üéÆ</div>
					<h3>Logic Puzzles</h3>
					<p>Solving Sudoku, chess problems, and brain teasers</p>
				</div>
				<div class="interest-card">
					<div class="interest-icon">üíª</div>
					<h3>Programming</h3>
					<p>Learning Python to solve mathematical problems computationally</p>
				</div>
				<div class="interest-card">
					<div class="interest-icon">üî¨</div>
					<h3>Science</h3>
					<p>Exploring physics and how math applies to the natural world</p>
				</div>
				<div class="interest-card">
					<div class="interest-icon">üìö</div>
					<h3>Reading</h3>
					<p>Enjoying books about mathematics, science, and problem-solving</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="contact-cta">
		<div class="cta-container">
			<h2>Let's Connect!</h2>
			<p>Have a math question or want to discuss a problem? I'd love to hear from you!</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get In Touch</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-hero {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		border-radius: 20px;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.profile-section {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.profile-image {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.avatar {
		width: 150px;
		height: 150px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #feca57 100%);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.3);
	}

	.avatar-text {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
	}

	.profile-name {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.profile-tagline {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.profile-stats {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.stat {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.stat-number {
		display: block;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #feca57;
	}

	.stat-label {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
	}

	.about-details {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.details-container, .interests-container, .cta-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.details-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.detail-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
	}

	.detail-card h2 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.detail-card p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.learning-list {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.learning-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.learning-icon {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.learning-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.learning-item p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.goals-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.goals-list li {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}

	.goals-list li::before {
		content: '‚úì';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #feca57;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.interests {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		color: white;
	}

	.interests-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.interest-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.interest-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.interest-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.interest-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.interest-card p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.contact-cta {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.cta-container h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.cta-container p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.btn {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #feca57 100%);
		color: white;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.3);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.4);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.profile-section {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			text-align: center;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.profile-name {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.profile-stats {
			justify-content: center;
		}

		.details-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.detail-card {
			padding: 2rem;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.avatar {
			width: 120px;
			height: 120px;
		}

		.avatar-text {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
	}
</style>
